# 🛗 Event-Driven Elevator Simulator

A professional Windows Forms-based elevator control system demonstrating event-driven architecture in C# .NET.

## Features

✅ **3-Floor Elevator System**
- Ground Floor (Floor 1)
- Floor 2  
- Floor 3

✅ **Event-Driven Architecture**
- Clean separation of concerns using C# events
- Non-blocking asynchronous operations
- Real-time event logging

✅ **Realistic UI Design**
- Visual elevator cars with opening/closing doors
- Control panel with floor buttons
- Digital floor display
- Comprehensive event log with timestamps

✅ **Smart Elevator Logic**
- Intelligent floor request queuing
- Automatic direction management (Up/Down/Idle)
- Door open/close simulation
- Pending request tracking

